    <sys:String x:Key="Setup.Launch.Visibility.CloseImmediately.Warning.Message">If the launcher is closed immediately after the game starts, features such as crash detection and changing the game title will be unavailable.&#x0a;To keep these features, you can choose to hide the launcher after the game starts and close it automatically after the game exits.</sys:String>
